Comment: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:31.73,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,===ED-CN===
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:31.73,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}看見誰都無法看見的夢{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:37.21,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}捨棄所有不需要的事物{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:40.51,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}無法割捨的感情{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:46.05,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}深藏在我的心裏{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:52.52,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}依然處在現實與理想的夾縫中{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:57.72,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}即使犧牲的枷鎖 栓住我的腳{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:22:02.86,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}無法壓抑滿腔的衝動{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:09.77,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}因為我有一顆強烈追求的心{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:15.51,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}虛偽 恐懼 虛飾 憂愁{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:21.05,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}面對各種負面情緒{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:26.56,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}我也不會弱到被擊垮{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:31.10,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}不知孤獨為何物 Trickster{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:39.53,Sub,,0,0,0,,秘密會議
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:43.27,Sub,,0,0,0,,聽起來好像他們每週五都會進行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:44.87,Sub,,0,0,0,,BINGO
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:47.97,Sub,,0,0,0,,今天的我可要立大功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.08,0:22:51.07,Sub,,0,0,0,,下一回 松田
